snippet.title: Domiverse - How to play - W8T
snippet.description:
How to play W8T

A planet populated by cowards jellyfish decided to make a clone of the last winner of the Domiverse to participate. It is how this robot is born.
W8T use his laser to burn enemies while flying trough the arena. He can surprise you with remote-controlled mines.

http://domiverse.be

Steam store: http://store.steampowered.com/app/598880/Domiverse/
